Package jteissler.csci1320.simplesql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Parser
    Parser interface which defines a parse method and documents which SQL methods should be supported by the parser.
    StringDatabase
    Simple SQL-like database methods which allow for tables with multiple columns of only string type data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssignmentParser
    Parses user input and determines what SQL command is being executed.
    Log
    A static utility class for logging buffered string to output files and to the terminal.
    Main
    The main class of the SQL system.
    Pair<L,R>
    A class which wraps two objects, allowing them to be grouped together.
    SQLDatabase
    A database implementation which creates databases as directories and individual tables as files within those directories.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SQLException
    Represents an exception that occurs while performing an SQL command.
